<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.4.7">
<l>kañcaṉ neñcuṅ kaṭumal laruñca kaṭamuṅkāliṉāl</l>
<l>tuñca veṉṟa cuṭarā ḻiyāṉvā ḻiṭameṉparāl</l>
<l>mañcu cērmā ḷikainī ṭakilpu kaiyumaṟaiyōr</l>
<l>ceñcol vēḷvip pukaiyuṅ kamaḻun teṉṉaraṅkamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They truly say that the place where lives the one with the shining discus,</l>
<l>Who conquered Kaṁsa’s heart, the vicious wrestlers,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the cart with his foot, so they perished,</l>
<l>Is Araṅkam of the South where copious smoke of aquila wood</l>
<l rend="indent">from cloud-enveloped mansions</l>
<l>And the smoke of sacrifices of the fine-spoken Vedic experts, scent [the air].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
